                            <container4
                                cq:styleIds="[1653545847150,1653242825678,1653545835982,1653545825686]"
                                jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/container/v2/container">
                                <text_copy
                                    cq:styleIds="[1659545825678]"
                                    jcr:created="{Date}2025-10-03T02:53:21.767-04:00"
                                    jcr:createdBy="singarx"
                                    jcr:lastModified="{Date}2025-12-05T00:40:34.757-05:00"
                                    jcr:lastModifiedBy="singarx"
                                    jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                    sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                                    text="&lt;p>&lt;b>SYDNEY, Australia, 29 May 2025 &lt;/b>– AbbVie (NYSE: ABBV) today announced Dr Carly Levetan has been appointed as Associate Medical Director, Oncology for Australia, to advance AbbVie’s efforts to transform standards of care in difficult to treat cancers.&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;Carly commenced in the role this month reporting to Lindsay Grant, Medical Director ANZ.&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;Carly comes to Abbvie with a background spanning clinical practice, medical affairs, and commercial strategy within the pharmaceutical and healthcare sectors in South Africa, Australia and Asia Pacific.&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;Carly holds a degree in Medicine and Surgery from University of Cape Town and has held leadership positions at Novartis and Johnson &amp;amp; Johnson, with a focus on hematology, oncology, medical excellence, and new product planning.&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;Carly played a central role in launching the first cell and gene therapies to patients in Australia, marking a significant milestone in treatment accessibility. More recently, she led a crossfunctional team to shape commercial strategy across oncology, immunology, neuroscience, and gene therapy. As a health consultant, Carly has also advised healthcare technology companies exploring the application of artificial intelligence in diagnostics.&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;“We are delighted to welcome Dr Carly Levetan to our team at AbbVie Australia. Carly will play a pivotal role in enhancing our strong oncology leadership, driving forward our patientfocused approach to delivering innovative therapies as we strive to transform lives and meet the needs of patients across Australia,” Medical Director ANZ, Lindsay Grant said.&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;“I am thrilled to join AbbVie Australia. My career has been dedicated to advancing healthcare innovation and improving patient outcomes, and I am excited to contribute to a team that shares this deep commitment. I’m looking forward to furthering AbbVie’s work in making innovative therapies accessible and impactful for patients,” Carly said.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;b>About AbbVie in Australia&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa; &lt;br>&#xd;&#xa; &lt;/b>AbbVie’s mission is to discover and deliver innovative medicines that solve serious health issues today and address the medical challenges of tomorrow. We strive to have a remarkable impact on people’s lives across several key therapeutic areas: immunology, oncology, neuroscience, eye care, virology and gastroenterology, in addition to products and services across its Allergan Aesthetics portfolio. For more information about AbbVie, please visit us at &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.abbvie.com.au/&quot;>www.abbvie.com.au&lt;/a>. Follow &lt;a href=&quot;https://x.com/abbvie_au&quot;>@abbvie_AU&lt;/a> on Twitter, &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.facebook.com/AbbVieAustralia/&quot;>Facebook&lt;/a>, &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.instagram.com/abbvieaustralia&quot;>Instagram&lt;/a> or our &lt;a href=&quot;https://LinkedIn.com/company/abbvie&quot;>LinkedIn&lt;/a> page.&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;b>Further details:&lt;/b>&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;a href=&quot;mailto:%20media_anz@abbvie.com&quot;>media_anz@abbvie.com&lt;/a>&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
